#test-modal-1.mfp-hide.white-popup-block
    h3 Description
    p Below the legal minimum tread depth do not condut a calibration. If there is the suspect for previous exchange special worn out  tyres, please note the tread depth on the backside of the calibration report.
      .clearfix
      a.button.large-button.primary.popup-modal-dismiss(href='#') Close

#test-modal-2.mfp-hide.white-popup-block
  h3 Description
  p With mixed tyres perform no calibration. Also note re-cut tyres on back side of the calibration report.
    .clearfix
    a.button.large-button.primary.popup-modal-dismiss(href='#') Close


#test-modal-3.mfp-hide.white-popup-block
  h3 Description
  p Tire pressure of all wheels (twin-tyred vehicles also the 'inner' wheels) on the drive shaft must correspond to the manufacturer's requirements. Adapt if required.
    .clearfix
    a.button.large-button.primary.popup-modal-dismiss(href='#') Close
